text: Andrey Lyskovets (born 7 October 1974) is a Belarusian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Belarus Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
